    public static class SAFSPlus.ScrollBar
extends SAFSPlus.Component
    Wrapper class providing APIs to handle ScrollBar keywords, like OneDown, PageDown, PageUp etc.

    • Method Detail

      • OneDown

        public static boolean OneDown(Component scrollbar,
                              java.lang.String... params)
        Attempts to perform a ScrollLineDown on a scrollbar.

        See Detailed Reference

        Parameters:
        scrollbar - Component (from App Map), a vertical scrollbar.
        params - optional
          params[0] steps int, The steps to scroll, must be positive.
        Returns:
        true if successful, false otherwise.
        See Also:
        SAFSPlus.prevResults, TestRecordData.getStatusCode(), TestRecordData.getStatusInfo()
        Example:
         
 boolean success = ScrollBar.OneDown(Map.Window.ScrollBar);//move 1 step down
 boolean success = ScrollBar.OneDown(Map.Window.ScrollBar, "5");//move 5 steps down
